About it reports Ukrinform with reference to [](https://www.saeima.lv/lv/aktualitates/saeimas-zinas/32112-ievies-valsts-aizsardzibas-dienestu).

It is envisaged that the first conscription to the ranks of the NSS military personnel will be constructed, recruits will begin service on July 1 this year.

