The Ministry of Veterans Affairs is working on the introduction of a veteran institute in Ukraine. The pilot project is currently planned in four -year -olds - Lviv, Vinnytsia, Dnipropetrovsk and Mykolaiv.

The Minister of Veterans of Ukraine Yulia Laputina announced this during a period of transmission on Ukrainian Radio on Wednesday, April 5.

